{
  "title": "Rich Silky French Sweet Basil Tarte Tatin",
  "description": "A briny and silky French dish featuring Thai sweet basil, perfect for a lazy Sunday, and low in carbs. This tarte tatin is a twist on the classic recipe, with a focus on sweet and savory flavors.",
