  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "In a large skillet, melt the butter over medium heat and cook the onions and garlic until softened.",
    "Add the chopped Thai sweet basil to the skillet and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the heavy cream, gruyere cheese, eggs, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add the cooked onion and basil mixture to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Pour the mixture into a 9-inch tart pan lined with almond flour.",
    "Bake the tarte tatin for 35 minutes, or until the edges are golden brown.",
    "Remove the tarte tatin from the oven and let it rest for 10 minutes before serving."
  ],
